# Midday â€” Buzzanator Mode

## Midday Gameplay / Focus Session

This is the reset point.

- Lock distractions out
- Focus on the single most important task
- Execute cleanly
- No multitasking
- No overthinking

Play the game in front of you.

---

## Lunch + Midday Recap

Pause.

Ask:
- What did I complete?
- What moved forward?
- What needs adjusting (not judging)?

Eat. Breathe. Reset.

Then continue.
# Night â€” Buzzanator Mode

## Wind Down
Slow the pace.
Lower the noise.
Release the day.

---

## Reflection
- What went well?
- What did I learn?
- What can wait until tomorrow?

No guilt. No replaying.

---

