Rest. The work continues tomorrow.

# Poster Export Notes

Recommended formats:
- Print: Letter & A4
- Phone wallpaper (lock screen safe margins)
- Instagram square
- Instagram story (vertical)
- Canvas / large poster

Design guidance:
- Palette: electric blue, white, cool grey
- Clean tech aesthetic
- Subtle glow edges
- No black / no gold
- Minimal typography

This text is canonical. Do not rewrite.

